=IF(B11<>"",_xlfn.LET(
    _xlpm.table, _xlfn._xlws.FILTER(AllWireOffsets[[Temp]:[Offset]],AllWireOffsets[traceability_no]=B11),
    _xlpm.temps,      INDEX(_xlpm.table,,1),
    _xlpm.offsets,    INDEX(_xlpm.table,,2),
    _xlpm.matches, _xlfn.VSTACK(
        _xlfn.XLOOKUP(NominalTemp, _xlpm.temps, _xlpm.table, NA(), -1),
        _xlfn.XLOOKUP(NominalTemp, _xlpm.temps, _xlpm.table, NA(), 1)
    ),
    IFERROR(
      _xlfn.XLOOKUP(NominalTemp, _xlpm.temps, _xlpm.offsets, NA(),0),
      QRound(_xlfn.FORECAST.LINEAR(NominalTemp, INDEX(_xlpm.matches,,2), INDEX(_xlpm.matches,,1)))
    )
),"")
